---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Customization — Spicetify">
  <div class="container docs">
    <aside class="docs-sidebar">
      <nav>
        <h4>Getting Started</h4>
        <a href="/docs/getting-started">Installation</a>
        <a href="/docs/customization" class="active">Customization</a>
        <a href="#">Development</a>
        <a href="#">FAQ</a>
      </nav>
    </aside>
    <article class="docs-content">
      <h1>Customization</h1>
      <p class="lead">Make Spotify look and feel exactly how you want with themes, extensions, and custom apps.</p>

      <h2>Themes</h2>
      <p>Themes change the entire visual appearance of Spotify. They can modify colors, fonts, spacing, layouts, and more. You can browse and install themes from the community-driven Marketplace.</p>
      <pre><code>kladen config current_theme "Nord"&#10;kladen apply</code></pre>

      <h2>Extensions</h2>
      <p>Extensions add new functionality to Spotify. They can provide keyboard shortcuts, enhance the UI, or integrate with external services.</p>
      <pre><code>kladen config extensions "shuffle+.js"&#10;kladen apply</code></pre>

      <h2>Custom Apps</h2>
      <p>Custom Apps are fully-featured pages that run inside Spotify. You can build your own or install existing ones from the Marketplace.</p>

      <h2>Colors and Schemes</h2>
      <p>You can customize individual colors without applying a full theme:</p>
      <pre><code>[color]&#10;main_fg = #ffffff&#10;main_bg = #000000&#10;accent = #1ed760&#10;subtext = #a1a1aa</code></pre>

      <h2>Marketplace</h2>
      <p>The Marketplace is the easiest way to discover and install community-made themes, extensions, and custom apps. Access it directly from within Spotify after installing the Marketplace extension.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .docs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    padding: 48px 24px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .docs-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
    height: fit-content;
  }

  .docs-sidebar h4 {
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .docs-sidebar a {
    display: block;
    padding: 6px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .docs-sidebar a:hover,
  .docs-sidebar a.active {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .docs-content h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .docs-content .lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .docs-content h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
  }

  .docs-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #d4d4d8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .docs-content pre {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .docs-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .docs-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
